Installation
------------

The easiest way to get $project is if you have setuptools_ installed::

	easy_install $project

Without setuptools, it's still pretty easy. Download the ${project}.tgz file from 
`$project's Cheeseshop page`_, untar it and run::

	python setup.py install

.. _$project's Cheeseshop page: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/$project/
.. _setuptools: http://peak.telecommunity.com/DevCenter/EasyInstall